Title: Listerine Ultraclean Access Flosser Refills - Mint
Description: Easily Gets to 100% of Hard of Reach Places®Mint FlavoredRemoves Tough Plaque that Brushing May MissDoes Not Contain Mouth Rinse IngredientsRefills compaitable forLISTERINE Ultraclean Access Flosser Starter Pack – Even though most people understand the importance of flossing, a significant percentage of the population avoids this oral care step because they consider it to be inconvenient. LISTERINE Ultraclean Access Flosser Starter Pack offers a way to floss more easily and more effectively. With its easy-to-use handle and replaceable heads, this flosser can help remove even the most difficult-to-reach plaque, which may reduce your risk of developing cavities and the gum disease gingivitis. Flossing Made EasyWinding a strip of floss around your fingers using the correct technique and then figuring out how to access the recesses between each individual tooth can be tricky, but the LISTERINE Ultraclean Access Flosser Starter Pack gets rid of all the guesswork. The reusable handle is ergonomically shaped and equipped with non-slip grip so that you can easily maneuver it around your mouth. Each head is strung with high-tenacity yarn that can scrape away plaque from between your teeth and below the gum line. Flossing is most effective when combined with other elements of a proper oral care routine such as brushing. Talk to your dentist if you have any questions or concerns. About LISTERINEDr. Joseph Lawrence and his partner Jordan Lambert developed a new antiseptic formula from four essential oils in 1879, and they decided to name their invention after Joseph Lister, a well-known physician who introduced sterile medical practices in the 1800s. The LISTERINE brand was born. Since its introduction, LISTERINE has been recommended by dentists and hygienists as one of the best brands to fight cavities and gum disease. Today, the brand is owned by Johnson & Johnson, and it has expanded beyond mouthwashes to also manufacture oral care products like floss, whitening strips, breath-freshening strips, and more.

Title: Torlen TOR 040 Hair Straightener
Description: The Torlen TOR 040 Hair Straightener has been designed to make sure you are left with straight and smooth hair minus all the extra effort. This straightener comes with several features which make sure that your hair looks absolutely stunning and doesn’t get damaged too. Ceramic Plates As this straightener comes with ceramic plates, you are left with straight and smooth hair due to even distribution of heat. The negative ions released by the ceramic plates help reduce the static electricity in your hair and make it frizz-free. Ceramic, Tourmaline Coating The ceramic and tourmaline coating helps control the frizz in your hair. Adding to this, the ceramic and tourmaline coating helps the straightener glide through your hair with ease. Sealing your cuticle layer and helping you retain the moisture are the negative ions released by the ceramic and tourmaline coating. 30 seconds Heat-up Time With a 30 seconds heat-up time, this straightener ensures you won’t be wasting much time on waiting for the straightener to get ready for use. Micro porous technology The micro porous technology helps lock the natural moisture in your hair and protects your hair from getting damaged or burnt. This makes your hair shiny and smooth. Ion Field Technology As this straightener comes with the ion field technology, all the natural oils and moisture in your hair gets retained. This prevents your hair from getting damaged or dry during the straightening process. Variable High Heat Setting  Allowing you to pick the temperature which best suits your hair type is the variable high heat setting of this straightener. This gives you complete control over the appliance and the temperature. Protects from damage This straightener protects your hair from damage by restoring the natural oils and moisture in your hair. Floating Flexible Plates Ensuring that equal pressure is applied on your hair and no dents or lines are left are the floating flexible plates of this straightener.
